  "original_title": "\u0db6\u0dda\u0dbb\u0dda \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dad\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dd4\u0d9a\u0dc5\u0dd0\u0dba\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d87\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dc5\u0dd4 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc4\u0db3\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dd0\u0db1\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dda \u0db4\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Two people, including a woman, are on a parade to identify a group of people who pushed them into the Beira lake",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Colombo Fort Magistrate Thilina Gamage today (23) ordered that a woman and a man arrested by the Special Investigation Unit for being violent and pushing a group of people into the Beira Lake after attacking the Colombo Gallumudoora activists will be remanded until the 26th for an identification parade.",
        "A woman and a man residing in Kollupitiya area were remanded.",
        "The Police Special Investigation Unit presented the facts to the court that these suspects, who were among the group who were behaving violently after attacking the Colombo Gallumudoora activists, pushed a group of people into Beira Lake on May 09.",
        "The police asked the court to allow the witnesses to present them in a parade to identify the suspects as the people who faced this incident have claimed to be able to identify the suspects."
      ],
